summary: peter has a lot more spidery habits than he initially lets on, because....no one could possibly relate and he doesn’t want to...
body:
peter has a lot more spidery habits than he initially lets on, because….no one could possibly relate and he doesn’t want to feel weird. but one day he realizes they pretty much all sound like shitposts so he just starts tweeting them out and gets big popular. 

like, not even on his spider-man twitter. @ peterbparkour tweets out something like “I’ve officially decided chewing is too much of a chore. excited to announce from now on I’ll release venom that melts all my food into a convenient liquid which I’ll then drink from a fun and sexy crazy straw” and it has 40 million replies that all say ‘same’ 

“just stubbed my toe really fucking bad so I’m gonna rip my leg off- hope it doesn’t take to long to grow back!’ ‘yea it be like that’

“to the man who just stole my backpack on the subway- sir please. please. my eggsack is in there. sir please. they’re just babies they’re scared they’ll devour you SIR PLEASE MY EGGSACK” ‘haha this guys wild’

“the temperature has started going down so it’s time for me to hibernate!!!! see you all in 7 months!!! :)” and someone goes ‘worm’ and he replies “spider, actually”

My classmates being rude. Noisy....

Me. My respect and care for humanity for the day is 100%.: oh look at how lovely this day is-

My classmates being rude. Noisy. Idiotic.annoying and just an disgrace to a CATHOLIC ORIENTED SCHOOL: oops. Lets eat candies and not throw the wrappers and the left overs in the proper trashcan cayse we have a janitor!

Me. And my respect for humanity has gone down to 90%: whats fucking new? Their pricks in anyday

A dryg seminar where a police tells you how bad drugs are for cause they cause you to cut yourself and shows pictures of people cutting themselves without warning and a thought about that picture might trigger someone: oops ny hand slipped

Me. Eye twitches. My care respect for humanity has gone to 70%: its fine. I’m fine its just a mistake. They probably were just rushing to get that finished right???

Me. Smiles with pain in my eyes. My respect for humanity is now gone to 45: go to hell-

Trump: exists

Me and my respect for humanity has gone to 25℅: ONE DAY I’LL GET THE CHANCE TO KILL YOU

Rude anons hurting my favorite people with rude and mean asks: i-

blog.name: alexandro-lima
blog.title: Alexandro Lima - Ilustrador
blog.description: Olá, bem vindo ao meu blog! Sou um ilustrador/arte finalista publicitário com larga experiência de mercado. Considero como seus “mestres inspiradores” Will Eisner, Jack Kirby, John Buscema e Canini. Sou um apreciador de quadrinhos, utilizo muito desta que é considerada a nona arte como fonte de referência para muitos de seus trabalhos.Mesclo trabalho à mão com vetorização e colorização digital em meus trabalhos. Realizo ilustrações, caricaturas, logotipos e pinturas. Este blog tem o objetivo de mostrar o que mais atual ando produzindo. Divulgue e opine!

summary:
Capitão América - Bucky Barnes

Revista Captain America Vol. 5 #34 - 2008

No dia 6 de fevereiro de 2007, após a conclusão do...
caption:
Capitão América - Bucky Barnes

Revista Captain America Vol. 5 #34 - 2008

No dia 6 de fevereiro de 2007, após a conclusão do arco Guerra Civil, o Capitão América foi morto, baleado num dos joelhos e no estômago, nas escadarias do Capitólio, a caminho do seu julgamento. Foi socorrido, mas morreu a caminho do hospital.

A “bandeira e o escudo” seriam ocupados por Bucky, que revivera pouco antes como o super-herói Soldado Invernal e fora parceiro do Capitão na II Guerra Mundial. Pela primeira vez o Capitão América (ou Bucky) irá usar como arma, além M1911A1 e uma faca, além de contar com recursos cibernéticos para amplificar sua força no braço esquerdo (com o qual ele segura o escudo).
